title: Kennedy.2015.08.19.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2

Kennedy kicks the night off with some talk about the Clinton email scandal. She and Ed Henry spar.

Ed Henry is here via satellite to discuss his exchange with Hillary Clinton.

Tonight we've got MICHAEL MALICE, TOM SHILLUE, KRISTEN SOLTIS ANDERSON and on our party panel. They keep up with the Hillary email scandal talk.

The panel returns to talk discuss Trump vs Hillary. (APOCALYPSE)

Trump wants to kick out all of the illegal immigrants - and their kids. JUDGE ANDREW NAPOLITANO is here to talk about how legally Trump can't do that. Afterwards they talk more Hillary email scandal. (Damn, this is a heavy Clinton ep.)

Our party panel is back to talk about the Ashley Madison hack. Afterwards they move onto the FDA approving a female Viagra. Next up - the most expensive colleges. At the top some school called "Harvey Mudd College". Weird.

Kennedy has founder of SPIN magazine BOB GUCCIONE, JR in studio to discuss the poor state of affairs in modern music, his temporary return to SPIN, and the commodification of music.

Nightcap: Jeb Bush & common core.
